          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In Table 7 the experimental and calculated",
                " K-factors (K=S1/S2 ,where A1 and A2 are the specific",
                " photopeak activities of the isotope investigated and",
                " comparator, respectively) for isotopes of Na-24,Sc-46,",
                " Cu-64,Ga-72, As-76, Sb-122 and comparators of Co-60,",
                " In-114m, Au-198 are compared."
